ResourceHeader.Description: Energetic Particle Detector (EPD), Energetic Ion Spectrometer (EIS) Electron Energy Spectra, Level 2, Quick-Look Survey, 2.42 s Data. The EIS provides ion composition measurements (protons versus oxygen ions) and angular distributions over the energy range from approximately 45 to 500 keV.
